The following is a list of Commands that are processed by the CFS Data Storage Application.

Global DS_ADD_MID_CC
Add Message ID To Packet Filter Table

Global DS_CLOSE_ALL_CC
Close All Destination Files

Global DS_CLOSE_FILE_CC
Close Destination File

Global DS_GET_FILE_INFO_CC
Get File Info Packet

Global DS_NOOP_CC
No-Operation Command

Global DS_RESET_CC
Reset Housekeeping Telemetry Counters Command

Global DS_SET_APP_STATE_CC
Set Enable/Disable State For DS Application

Global DS_SET_DEST_AGE_CC
Set Max File Age For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_DEST_BASE_CC
Set Basename For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_DEST_COUNT_CC
Set Sequence Count For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_DEST_EXT_CC
Set Extension For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_DEST_PATH_CC
Set Pathname For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_DEST_SIZE_CC
Set Max File Size For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_DEST_STATE_CC
Set Ena/Dis State For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_DEST_TYPE_CC
Set Filename Type For Destination File Table Entry

Global DS_SET_FILTER_FILE_CC
Set Destination File For Packet Filter Table Entry

Global DS_SET_FILTER_PARMS_CC
Set Algorithm Parameters For Packet Filter Table Entry

Global DS_SET_FILTER_TYPE_CC
Set Filter Type For Packet Filter Table Entry
